## Success Rate SLOs
"checkout":
  Guarantees 99.95% over 30d window as measured by "api_availability" with: {}

"payment":
  Guarantees 99.99% over 30d window as measured by "api_availability" with: {}

"checkout_p99":
  Guarantees 99.9% over 30d window as measured by "api_latency" with: { threshold_ms: 500 }

"checkout_rps":
  Guarantees 99.9% over 30d window as measured by "api_throughput" with: { threshold_rps: 1000 }
